text: Żebbuġ Rovers Football Club is a football club from the village of Żebbuġ, Gozo. The club was founded in 1975 and is named for the village of Żebbuġ. They currently play in the Second Division of Gozo Football League. == References == Category:Football clubs in Malta Category:Association football clubs established in 1975 Category:1975 establishments in Malta Category:Żebbuġ, Gozo
